item.title: Medic Kings toppled by Imperial Might
item.author: David R Nielsen-Scott,
item.description: Imperial hosted Kings’ Medics at Harlington, looking for a win to bounce back from a disappointing defeat last week. IC got off to a bright start, dominating possession, territory and hitting hard in the contact. However, errors crept in at crucial stages, allowing the unspoilt Kings’ tryline to …
